Package: com.nileshkale.deviceidchangerios
Name: NK DeviceID Changer (iOS)
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Description: Authorized-testing tool that spoofs identifierForVendor (IDFV) per target app on a jailbroken iPhone, for exercising device-binding / fraud-scoring / reinstall-detection logic during pentest engagements. Rootless (Dopamine/palera1n) only. See companion frida/ios_device_id_hook.js for IDFA/Keychain-UUID/carrier-info hooking.
Maintainer: Nilesh Kale
Author: Nilesh Kale
